title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 24 2022
description:
Rep. Jim Jordan on what this election is all about. DOJ's big announcement turns out to be a nothing burger about China. Clay gives House of the Dragon a B grade. Biden zones out in interview. Biden's insane closing argument in favor of the transgender agenda for kids. Female high school volleyball player seriously injured by male playing girl's sport. Clay has said he will debate anyone in the country on the women's sports-transgender issue. Clay and Buck welcome Catalina Lauf, Congressional candidate in the 11th District of Illinois. ABC political director Rick Klein says Arizona could swing the Senate. MSNBC host Tiffany Cross smears diverse GOP candidates. Poll shows affirmative action in college admissions is hugely unpopular.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
